## DEFAULT\_APIDOCS\_EXTRACTION\_PATH variable

Default path as the output directory for extracted api reports and models

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
DEFAULT_APIDOCS_EXTRACTION_PATH = "docs/apidocs"
```
